  "text": "To examine if there was any long-term trends in tropospheric ozone over these cities we did regression analysis of tropospheric ozone using trend model, details of which are given elsewhere [CITATION_1] and hence described here briefly. Error estimates are according to [CITATION_2] . In order to remove the effects of natural sources of ozone variability such as 11-year solar cycle as well as the linear trend in solar irradiance we use a regression model. It consists of seasonal cycle, linear trend and solar cycle. The general expression for the regression model equation can be written as follows:",
